OL,3,CAre three new Merseyrail train
OL,4,Cstations on the way?
OL,6,FMetro Mayor Steve Rotheram says it
OL,7,Fwill better connect communities with
OL,8,FLiverpool and the rest of the country.
OL,9,FITV Granada Reports journalist
OL,10,FJennifer Buck caught up with him
OL,11,Fearlier.
OL,13,FPlans for the biggest expansion of the
OL,14,FMerseyrail network for decades have
OL,15,Fbeen put forward - with proposals for
OL,16,Fthree new train stations.
OL,18,FThe announcement comes as part of
OL,19,FLiverpool City Region Mayor Steve
OL,20,FRotheram's campaign launch for a re-
OL,21,Felection to a third term.
