OL,3,CAre three new Merseyrail train
OL,4,Cstations on the way?
OL,6,FIf successful he plans to build new
OL,7,Fstations at Daresbury in Halton, Carr
OL,8,FMill in St Helens and Woodchurch on
OL,9,Fthe Wirral.
OL,11,FIt is a part of Mr Rotheram's pledge
OL,12,Fto connect historically underserved
OL,13,Fcommunities to the local rail network,
OL,14,Fand means that every borough of the
OL,15,Fcity region will have had a brand-new
OL,16,Fstation.
OL,18,FSteve Rotheram said: "Any modern,
OL,19,Fthriving region is only as good as its
OL,20,Fpublic transport.
