OL,3,CAre three new Merseyrail train
OL,4,Cstations on the way?
OL,6,F"Since I've been Mayor, I've worked
OL,7,Faround the clock to give our region
OL,8,Fwhat Londoners get to enjoy every day:
OL,9,Fa reliable, accessible, affordable and
OL,10,Fintegrated network that helps, rather
OL,11,Fthan hinders people getting about.
OL,13,F"But I know that in some parts of our
OL,14,Fregion, Liverpool can feel as distant
OL,15,Fand inaccessible as London.
OL,17,F"I'm working to put that right,
OL,18,Fbringing local people closer to each
OL,19,Fother and to the opportunities we're
OL,20,Fcreating."
