OL,3,CAre three new Merseyrail train
OL,4,Cstations on the way?
OL,6,FSince he was elected in 2017, Mr
OL,7,FRotheram has voiced ambitions to
OL,8,Frevolutionise the region's local rail
OL,9,Fnetwork with a London-style system.
OL,11,FIf re-elected, the Mayor has also
OL,12,Fpledged to complete the new #100m
OL,13,FLiverpool Baltic station by 2027, a
OL,14,Ffull year ahead of its current
OL,15,Fschedule, as well as regenerating
OL,16,FMoorfields station and upgrading the
OL,17,Fentrances.
