OL,3,CAre three new Merseyrail train
OL,4,Cstations on the way?
OL,6,FOther proposals include plans to
OL,7,Fdeliver a seven-day network with
OL,8,Fincreased timetable provision at
OL,9,Fweekends and evenings by 2028.
OL,11,FMayor Rotheram was unanimously
OL,12,Freselected as Labour's candidate for
OL,13,FLiverpool City Region Mayor last year
OL,14,Fand has twice been elected with well
OL,15,Fover 50% of the vote.
OL,17,FThe Mayoral election will take place
OL,18,Fon Thursday 2 May 2024.
